## Description {#details}

This struct is used by <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/telemetry/telemetryinfo">TelemetryInfo</a> to support isa&lt;&gt;, dyn&#95;cast&lt;&gt; operations.

It is defined as a struct (rather than an enum) because it is expected to be extended by subclasses which may have additional <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/telemetry/telemetryinfo">TelemetryInfo</a> types defined to describe different events.
